; Coverage for xact.cc lines 1104-1111 (format expression in auto_xact account)
; When an auto transaction account contains %(expression), the format
; expression is evaluated to determine the account name.

= Expenses
    (Budget:%(account))    -1

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Budget
24-Jan-01 Test                  (Budget:Expenses:Food)      $-10.00      $-10.00
end test
